- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with improving the efficiency of neural networks, which is a key area of research in AI. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is less likely but still possible as the proposed approach could potentially be applied to sparsify recurrent neural networks used in image or video processing tasks. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also less likely but possible as the paper deals with sparsification of neural networks, which is a key area of research in this category.
